name: coloredlogs
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "9.1" %}

package:
  name: coloredlogs
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/c/coloredlogs/coloredlogs-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6ac9a61034e17e2bb6dcd61e63b6f628ca9302a349ec049d220a76928bc149c7

build:
  number: 1
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .
  entry_points:
    - coloredlogs = coloredlogs.cli:main

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
    - humanfriendly >=4.7
  run:
    - python
    - humanfriendly >=4.7
    - colorama  # [win]

test:
  imports:
    - coloredlogs
  commands:
    - coloredlogs --help  # [not osx]

about:
  home: https://coloredlogs.readthedocs.org
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Colored terminal output for Python's logging module

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - andfoy
    - ccordoba12
